         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged by instrument: strings, woodwinds, brass, percussion.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains orchestral parts (not scores) that belonged to the Beethoven Society of Providence, Rhode Island. Most of the music was composed in the nineteenth century; a few pieces are from the eighteenth century. A variety of genres are represented, chiefly dances, overtures, and symphonies.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
